---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import logo from '../images/logo.png'
---

<article class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center md:gap-2 pt-10 justify-between relative"> 
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-8 max-md:items-center">
    <h1 class="md:leading-snug lg:leading-snug leading-tight lg:text-6xl md:text-5xl max-md:text-center text-5xl font-black font-heading animate-moveBanner">Keep Your Property Looking its Best</h1>
    <p class="text-xl transition animate-moveBanner">
      Locally owned Tommy Tree Stump, LLC will keep your property attractive and safe with professional tree services. We specialize in competitively priced stump removal. We will come to your location to bid on the project and keep your property protected while we work. 
    </p>
    <span class="font-bold text-xl animate-moveBanner">FREE estimate.</span>
    <button class="bg-black cursor-pointer transition hover:bg-neutral-700 active:bg-black text-neutral-100 w-44 px-4 py-2 text-2xl rounded-lg animate-moveBanner font-bold tracking-wide">Contact Us</button>
  </div>
  <Image src={logo} alt="a tree stump" class="w-[50%] max-md:w-full max-md:-mt-5 animate-moveBanner" /> 
</article>
  


